p.d: It’s time for some Bucharest nights and there’s no better place to experience it than Private Gold, Romanian Romance. Meet the spectacular MILF Ginger Devil, an incredible blonde that you won’t be able to take your eyes off. Or take a late night walk with tour guide Cherry Kiss, a private journey that will show you the best the city has to offer, herself. Nilla Black will also be reunited with her long lost cousin and celebrate the reunion with some night time fun. Meanwhile the legendary Rose Delight has more than just words for her photographer and veteran David Perry. And finally we will meet Lulu Love, a cute girl that makes the most of a situation when she finds a stranger in her hotel room. Private Gold, Romanian Romance, you won’t want to miss it.
